---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const jsonLD = { '@context': 'https://schema.org', '@type': 'WebPage', name: 'Terms & Disclaimer' };
const updated = '2026-07-02';
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms & Disclaimer" description="Terms of use and disclaimer for VisaLang." jsonLD={jsonLD} noindex={true}>
  <main class="page-shell">
    <article class="guide-article narrow-page">
        <p class="eyebrow">Legal</p>
        <h1>Terms &amp; Disclaimer</h1>
        <p class="guide-summary">Last updated: {updated}</p>

        <h2>Independent information site</h2>
        <p>VisaLang (flowlight.me) is an independent language-exam navigation website. We are <strong>not</strong> a government authority, exam owner, immigration lawyer, visa agency, or educational institution. Content is for general informational purposes only.</p>

        <h2>No legal or immigration advice</h2>
        <p>Nothing on this site constitutes legal, financial, tax, or immigration advice. Visa requirements, exam fees, test dates, accepted certificates, and government policies change frequently and vary by jurisdiction. Always verify requirements with the official exam owner or government authority before booking an exam or filing an application.</p>

        <h2>Accuracy</h2>
        <p>We make a good-faith effort to keep guides accurate and up to date. Each guide shows a Last Updated date. However, we make no warranties about completeness or accuracy. If you find an error, please <a href="/contact/">contact us</a>.</p>

        <h2>External links</h2>
        <p>Guides link to official sources (exam providers, government sites) and occasionally to third-party preparation resources. We are not responsible for the content or practices of external sites.</p>

        <h2>Affiliate disclosure</h2>
        <p>Some links to preparation products or courses may be affiliate links, meaning we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you. These are clearly labeled. See our <a href="/affiliate-disclosure/">Affiliate Disclosure</a> for details. We never recommend a product before the official-source guidance on a page.</p>

        <h2>Acceptable use</h2>
        <p>You agree not to scrape, copy, or redistribute VisaLang content at scale, and not to use the site for any unlawful purpose.</p>

        <h2>Limitation of liability</h2>
        <p>To the maximum extent permitted by law, VisaLang and its operators are not liable for any loss or damage arising from reliance on site content, including decisions about exams, visas, or immigration applications.</p>

        <h2>Changes to terms</h2>
        <p>We may update these terms. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance.</p>

        <p class="compliance-line">VisaLang is an independent publication. Always confirm requirements with the official source before booking.</p>
        <p class="last-updated">Last updated: {updated}</p>
    </article>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
